rows.label: bf05400150_0010
rows.name: Meleph-sama, greetings. I have news from the front.

rows.label: bf05400150_0020
rows.name: We received a report that it has crossed the central buffer line.

rows.label: bf05400150_0030
rows.name: It's advancing at about forty titanpeds per hour!

rows.label: bf05400150_0040
rows.name:
Hmm.
I want to get in front of it.

rows.label: bf05400150_0050
rows.name: Is there a suitable place to dock?

rows.label: bf05400150_0070
rows.name:
From there,
you should be able to reach the cliff above its path.
